{"tid":351986,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個忍屎/忍唔到屎嘅難忘經歷","createTime":"2017-08-08T12:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T03:05:32.000Z","uid":5469,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b082037f799622c443a9a6fbb6cd6fd20dd35dca","tid":351986,"uid":5469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:53:05.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前細細個小一左右，我屋企同媽媽個邊啲親戚隔兩三個月都會去一齊涌尾（船灣淡水湖嗰邊）BBQ。每次臨走之前，姨丈都會帶我地幾個細路去「片石仔」，我次次都好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一次，我BBQ嗰陣好似食左啲唔熟嘅嘢，之後好肚痛好想痾爛屎。正想我去廁所嗰陣，姨丈：「邊個跟我落去玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」我心諗如果去屙屎下次就要等三個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以我就跟左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一邊片石一邊忍，大佬肚痛點忍，最後就瀨晒落條底褲度、有幾滴屎汁滴左落地，同時我成個屎忽感覺好暖、個鼻聞到好撚臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後啊媽一邊幫我清理一邊鬧到我飛起，好難忘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f66dc77fa5e556d0247007101c2fe4ff6a1d86","tid":351986,"uid":133627,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:07:06.000Z","msg":"我有一個壞習慣 就係成日放屁<br />\n有一日 我就有d肚痛 但係未到要痾既地步 忍住先 諗住遲d一次過痾晒佢 <br />\n與此同時 我又想放屁 咁咪放囉 <br />\n點知<br />\n呢個屁特別臭 個pat pat又暖暖地<br />\n心諗 唔L係呀嘛 <br />\n就衝左入廁所 見到條底褲有pat屎<br />\n我就無樓上咁好彩有呀媽幫手洗 我要自己洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm